(
<emphasis box="[246,369,507,530]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="749">Parexogone</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[386,516,506,530]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="749">meridionalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[523,654,506,530]" pageId="26" pageNumber="749" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is similar to the species 
<emphasis box="[932,949,507,530]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="749">E</emphasis>
